name: Pure XS
description: Pure XS For Her by Paco Rabanne is a Oriental Floral fragrance for women. This is a new fragrance. Pure XS For Her was launched in 2018. Pure XS For Her was created by Quentin Bisch and Emilie (Bevierre) Coppermann.The fragrance Pure XS For Her is available as a 30ml Eau de Parfum, 50ml Eau de Parfum and 80ml Eau de Parfum.
content: Popocorn  Vanilla  Ylang-Ylang  Coconut  Peach  Orange Blossom  Ambrette (Musk Mallow)  White Musk  Sandalwood  Amberwood

name: Davidoff Cool Water
description: Cool Water by Davidoff is a Aromatic Aquatic fragrance for men. Cool Water was launched in 1988. The nose behind this fragrance is Pierre Bourdon.
content: Top notes are Sea water, Lavender, Mint, Green Notes, Rosemary, Calone and Coriander; middle notes are Sandalwood, Geranium, Jasmine and Neroli; base notes are Musk, Tobacco, Oakmoss, Cedar and Amber.

name: Versace Eros
description: Eros was launched in 2012. The nose behind this fragrance is Aurelien Guichard.
content: Top notes are Mint, Green Apple and Lemon; middle notes are Tonka Bean, Ambroxan and Geranium; base notes are Madagascar Vanilla, Virginian Cedar, Atlas Cedar, Vetiver and Oakmoss.

name: Versace Vanitas
description: Vanitas by Versace is a Floral fragrance for women. Vanitas was launched in 2011. The nose behind this fragrance is Dora Baghriche.
content: Top note is Lime; middle notes are Tiare Flower and Freesia; base notes are Virginia Cedar and Tonka Bean.

name: Burberry Her
description: Burberry Her by Burberry is a Floral Fruity Gourmand fragrance for women. This is a new fragrance. Burberry Her was launched in 2018. The nose behind this fragrance is Francis Kurkdjian.
content: Top notes are Strawberry, Raspberry, Blackberry, Sour Cherry, Black Currant, Mandarin Orange and Lemon; middle notes are Violet and Jasmine; base notes are Musk, Vanilla, Oakmoss, Cashmeran, Woody Notes, Amber and Patchouli.

name: Burberry London
description: London by Burberry is a Floral fragrance.  London was launched in 2006. London was created by Dominique Ropion and Jean-Marc Chaillan.
content: Top notes are Honeysuckle, Tangerine and Rose; middle notes are Jasmine, Tiare Flower, Peony and Clementine; base notes are Musk, Sandalwood and Patchouli.

name: Chloé
description: Chloe Eau de Parfum by Chloé is a Floral fragrance. Chloe Eau de Parfum was launched in 2008. Chloe Eau de Parfum was created by Amandine Clerc-Marie and Michel Almairac.
content: Top notes are Peony, Litchi and Freesia; middle notes are Rose, Lily-of-the-Valley and Magnolia; base notes are Virginia Cedar and Amber.

name: Black Opium
description: Black Opium is a Oriental Vanilla fragrance for women. Black Opium was launched in 2014. Black Opium was created by Nathalie Lorson, Marie Salamagne, Olivier Cresp and Honorine Blanc.
content: Top notes are Pear, Pink Pepper and Orange Blossom; middle notes are Coffee, Jasmine, Bitter Almond and Licorice; base notes are Vanilla, Patchouli, Cedar and Cashmere Wood.

name: Miracle
description: A Floral fragrance by Lancome. Miracle was launched in 2000. Miracle was created by Harry Fremont and Alberto Morillas.
content: Top notes are Litchi and Freesia; middle notes are Magnolia, Pepper, Ginger, Mandarin Orange and Jasmine; base notes are Jasmine, Musk and Amber.

name: L'Interdit
description: L'Interdit Eau de Parfum Intense by Givenchy is a Oriental Floral fragrance for women.  This is a new fragrance. L'Interdit Eau de Parfum Intense was launched in 2020. L'Interdit Eau de Parfum Intense was created by Dominique Ropion,  Anne Flipo and Fanny Bal.
content: Top note is Black Pepper; middle notes are Tuberose, Sesame and Orange Blossom; base notes are Madagascar Vanilla,  Patchouli and Vetiver

name: Silence Des Calanques
description: Silence Des Calanques by Aemium is a Oriental Floral fragrance for women and men. This is a new fragrance.  Silence Des Calanques was launched in 2021.
content: Top notes are Algae, Bergamot, Grapefruit and Mint; middle notes are Orange Blossom, Jasmine, Neroli and Solar notes;  base notes are Vetiver, Sandalwood, Tonka Bean and Cedar.

name: Orphéon
description: Orphéon by Diptyque is a Woody Chypre fragrance for women and men. This is a new fragrance. Orphéon was launched in 2021.
content: Top note is Juniper Berries; middle note is Jasmine; base notes are Cedar, Powdery Notes and Tonka Bean.

name: Moustache
description: Moustache Eau de Parfum by Rochas is a Oriental Woody fragrance for men. This is a new fragrance. Moustache Eau de Parfum was launched in 2018. The nose behind this fragrance is Nathalie Gracia-Cetto.
content: Top notes are Pink Pepper and Mandarin Orange; middle notes are Atlas Cedar and Bulgarian Rose; base notes are Benzoin, Vanilla and Patchouli.

name: Prada Amber
description: Prada Amber Pour Homme (Prada Man) by Prada is a Oriental Fougere fragrance for men. Prada Amber Pour Homme (Prada Man) was launched in 2006.  The nose behind this fragrance is Daniela (Roche) Andrier
content: Top notes are Neroli, Cardamom, Bergamot and Mandarin Orange; middle notes are Myrrh, Musk, Orange Blossom, Geranium and Vetiver;  base notes are Saffron,Vanilla, Labdanum, Leather, Tonka Bean, Sandalwood and Patchouli.

name: Tommy
description: Tommy by Tommy Hilfiger is a Citrus Aromatic fragrance for men. Tommy was launched in 1995.  Tommy was created by Annie Buzantian and Alberto Morillas.
content: Top notes are Mint, Bergamot, Grapefruit and Lavender; middle notes are Granny Smith apple, Cranberry and Rose;  base notes are Cotton Flower, Cactus and Amber.

name: Bad Boy
description: Bad Boy by Carolina Herrera is a Oriental Spicy fragrance for men. This is a new fragrance. Bad Boy was launched in 2019. Bad Boy was created by Quentin Bisch and Louise Turner.
content: Top notes are White Pepper, Black Pepper and Bergamot; middle notes are Sage and Cedar; base notes are Tonka Bean, Cacao and Amberwood.

name: Black Xs for Men
description: Black XS by Paco Rabanne is a Oriental Woody fragrance for men.  Black XS was launched in 2005. Black XS was created by Olivier Cresp and Rosendo Mateu.
content: Top notes are Lemon and Sage; middle notes are Praline, Cinnamon, Tolu Balsam and Black Cardamom;  base notes are Brazilian Rosewood, Patchouli and Black Amber.

name: Good Girl Suprême
description: Good Girl Suprême by Carolina Herrera is a Oriental Floral fragrance for women.  This is a new fragrance. Good Girl Suprême was launched in 2020.
content: The nose behind this fragrance is Louise Turner. Top notes are Forest Fruits and Egyptian Jasmine;  middle notes are Tonka Bean and Tuberose; base note is Vetiver.

name: Bottega Veneta
description: Bottega Veneta by Bottega Veneta is a Chypre Floral fragrance for women. Bottega Veneta was launched in 2011.  The nose behind this fragrance is Michel Almairac.
content: Top notes are Pink Pepper and Bergamot; middle note is Jasmine; base notes are Leather, oak moss and Patchouli.

name: Jaguar
description: Jaguar is a Aromatic Fougere fragrance for men. Jaguar was launched in 2002.
content: Top notes are Star Anise, Juniper Berries, Orange, Mandarin Orange, Lavender, Bergamot and Basil; middle notes are Ginger, Lotus and Orange Blossom; base notes are White Musk, Sandalwood and Benzoin.

name: Black XS for Her
description: lack XS for Her by Paco Rabanne is a Floral Woody Musk fragrance for women. Black XS for Her was launched in 2007. Black XS for Her was created by Emilie (Bevierre) Coppermann and Mark Buxton.
content: Top notes are Cranberry, Pink Pepper and Tamarind; middle notes are Cacao, Rose and Black Violet; base notes are Vanilla, Patchouli and Massoia Wood.
